      "id": "4f1ab90d-9f1b-4ee6-badb-7ce8804f37a7",
      "name": "Website Generation (8 Templates)",
      "content": "<p>Turn any outline or subtree into a professional website. Access via Share > Website format.</p>",
      "type": "chapter",
      "parentId": "0855ebbc-563f-40a1-a524-55b6b5c69833",
      "childrenIds": [
        "098bac1f-9e36-48a5-b1f7-41f8751c0152",
