      "id": "2dc087cb-6b6e-4d56-8b66-5401100f4df6",
      "name": "Node Actions",
      "content": "<p>Add Sibling Node, Rename, Collapse/Expand, Create Content for Descendants (AI), Share Subtree As...</p>",
